org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode

Class LeaseManager.Lease

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode.LeaseManager.Lease
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<LeaseManager.Lease>
    Enclosing class:
    LeaseManager

     class LeaseManager.Lease
extends Object
implements Comparable<LeaseManager.Lease>
    A Lease governs all the locks held by a single client. For each client there's a corresponding lease, whose timestamp is updated when the client periodically checks in. If the client dies and allows its lease to expire, all the corresponding locks can be released.
